.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/097-track-review/review/logs/iter-7.stderr:3329:opencode's project-level skill discovery looks for `.opencode/skills/` (plural per `https://opencode.ai/docs/skills`). This repo uses `.opencode/skills/` (singular), so opencode's built-in discovery silently fails. Every `opencode run` dispatch prints "Could not find any skills directories" before falling through to the `opencode-skills` plugin's bridging behavior.
